---------------------------------------------------------------------
 HashAggregate (actual rows=2 loops=1)
   Group Key: r1, count(r1) OVER (?)
   ->  WindowAgg (actual rows=2000 loops=1)
         ->  Index Scan using t_pkey on t (actual rows=2000 loops=1)
(4 rows)

